            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1628675758101-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1628675758101-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1628675775438-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
